---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Case Studies | MyHomePage">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-slate-950">Case Studies</h1>
  <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6">
    <article class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand">Case Study 01</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950">From task list to integrated site foundation</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">Consolidated the rebuild, page architecture, reusable components, access gate, and privacy requirements into one deployable pull request.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand">Case Study 02</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950">Safe document preview strategy</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">Documents are represented as metadata and placeholders. Sensitive files should remain in controlled storage, not in the static public folder.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
